metadata.name: Kool Kittens #1
metadata.description: Kool Kittens is a collection of 3333 NFTs, unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. This project was inspired to combat a growing trend of overpriced NFTs pricing many users out of the market. If you missed out on the opportunity to mint big projects, now is your chance to get in during the mint stage.Ownership provides access to supporting an ever-growing community of NFT enthusiasts and access to the latest Alpha across the Crypto space, not just NFTs. NOT affiliated with Cool Cats NFT or any organization.
